        "type": "text",
        "content": "PROGRAM+- Specify the complete path and program name to be executed"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "when this option is selected.  It is advisable to include the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "file extension, in order to differentiate CMD files from EXE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "files, etc."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PARMS+- The PARMS field may be used to control operation of the"
      },
      {
